Regression: FAIL_038 — timeout='' used to flow through to the wait loop and
report 'Waiting timeout exceeded' while the table got created. Empty option
values are now rejected up-front.

––– input –––
export INSTANCE=1
––– output –––
––– block: ../../base/replication/start-searchd-precach –––
––– input –––
mysql -h0 -P1306 -e "create table t38(id bigint, title text) shards='2' rf='1' timeout='';"
––– output –––
ERROR 1064 (42000) at line 1: Parameter 'timeout' requires to have a value
––– input –––
mysql -h0 -P1306 -e "show tables like 't38';"
